<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Help - IIIF Static Choices 2.5D</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="/css/styles.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1 class="mb-4">User guide - IIIF Static Choices | GUI</h1>
        
        <div class="row mb-4">
            <div class="col-md-12">
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-header bg-warning">
                        <h3 class="card-title mb-0">Steps to create the viewer</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <ol class="list-group list-group-numbered">
                            <li class="list-group-item d-flex justify-content-between align-items-start">
                                <div class="ms-2 me-auto">
                                    <div class="fw-bold">Prepare the images</div>
                                    Make sure you have both the albedo and the normal map of the object.
                                </div>
                            </li>
                            <li class="list-group-item d-flex justify-content-between align-items-start">
                                <div class="ms-2 me-auto">
                                    <div class="fw-bold">Upload both images</div>
                                    Drag or select the files in the web interface.
                                </div>
                            </li>
                            <li class="list-group-item d-flex justify-content-between align-items-start">
                                <div class="ms-2 me-auto">
                                    <div class="fw-bold">Complete metadata</div>
                                    Add title, description, and other object information.
                                </div>
                            </li>
                            <li class="list-group-item d-flex justify-content-between align-items-start">
                                <div class="ms-2 me-auto">
                                    <div class="fw-bold">Generate the viewer</div>
                                    Click on the "Generate" button and wait for the images to be processed.
                                </div>
                            </li>
                            <li class="list-group-item d-flex justify-content-between align-items-start">
                                <div class="ms-2 me-auto">
                                    <div class="fw-bold">Share the viewer</div>
                                    Use the generated link to share your 2.5D model.
                                </div>
                            </li>
                        </ol>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        

        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-12 text-center">
                <a href="/" class="btn btn-primary">Return to generator</a>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer mt-5">
            <p>Developed to facilitate the creation of viewers with <a href="https://github.com/bodleian/archiox-mirador-plugin" target="_blank">ArchiOX Relight Plugin</a> technology</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>